WEBVTT

00:00:28.300 --> 00:00:30.847
Vijana walienda barabarani,

00:00:30.871 --> 00:00:32.697
walikuwa na migomo.

00:00:32.721 --> 00:00:34.738
Na vijana wengi walifariki

00:00:35.627 --> 00:00:37.428
SAS: Tulipanda gari.

00:00:37.452 --> 00:00:38.652
Lilikuwa limejaa sana

00:00:38.676 --> 00:00:41.181
Watu walikimbia kunusuru maisha yao,

00:00:41.205 --> 00:00:43.662
Hivi ndivyo nilivyochipuruka Somalia.

00:00:44.221 --> 00:00:45.685
Mama yangu alinimisi sana.

00:00:45.709 --> 00:00:47.780
Hakuna yeyote aliyemweleza nilikokwenda.

00:00:48.520 --> 00:00:50.554
NDD:Ukweli ni kwamba, 
hatukusoma,

00:00:50.578 --> 00:00:53.309
Hatukuweza kwenda sokoni,
tulibaki nyumbani tu

00:00:53.333 --> 00:00:57.937
ikanifanya nijue kuwa ningepata 
nafasi ya kuchagua kitu kizuri,

00:00:57.961 --> 00:01:00.855
ningeweza kukichagua na kuwa na
maisha bora mbeleni.